article_title: Authorities Investigate Arson After Four Cars Set On Fire In OKC - News9.com - Oklahoma City, OK - News, Weather, Video and Sports
article_text:
Arson investigators are on the scene at 102nd St. and McKinley Ave. in Oklahoma City, after four cars were apparently set on fire overnight.

Neighbors at the location said this isn't the first time this has happened recently. The damage to the cars did not appear extensive.

No one was injured. Fire officials are investigating the incident as an arson.
